  <sys:String x:Key="UI_Playback_UrlFormat_Note">You can enter a full URL or a parameter-only segment (e.g. ?playseek=${(b)yyyyMMddHHmmss}-${(e)yyyyMMddHHmmss}); parameter-only will be auto-appended to the channel's live URL. Supports ${(b)...} / ${(e)...} / {utc:...} / {utcend:...} placeholders.</sys:String>
